    <h3>Top Refrigeration Brands in India</h3>
    <p><strong>Blue Star:</strong> India's most trusted commercial refrigeration brand. Excellent service network across India. Wide range of display chillers and under-counter units. Mid-to-premium pricing.</p>
    <p><strong>Voltas (Tata):</strong> Good quality Indian brand with strong service network. Slightly more affordable than Blue Star. Widely used in Indian food service.</p>
    <p><strong>Carrier Midea:</strong> Strong in commercial refrigeration. Good warranty terms and pan-India service.</p>
    <p><strong>Foster (UK) / Williams (UK):</strong> Premium commercial refrigeration brands used in high-end cafés and hotels. Available through importers in Delhi, Mumbai, Bengaluru.</p>
