    <h3>Furniture Buying Tips for Indian Café Owners</h3>
    <p>For most budget and mid-range cafés, local furniture fabricators in your city will offer the best value — especially for benches, counters, and custom seating. Get three quotes, check material quality (MDF vs solid wood vs metal), and ask to see sample pieces before ordering a full set.</p>
    <p>For chairs, major wholesale markets in Delhi (Kirti Nagar furniture market), Mumbai (Bhuleshwar, Santacruz), and Chennai (Anna Nagar) offer good quality at wholesale prices. For a 30-cover café, budget ₹2.5–₹4 lakh for a complete furniture set at mid-range quality.</p>

